# OperatorOS — Phase 1 marketing/demo site. Every variable below is optional;
# the app builds and runs with none of them set. See platform/README.md for the
# Phase 2 SaaS platform's env vars (Postgres, Clerk) — not needed here.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------ AI (Business DNA generation — ADR-0016)
# OpenAI powers the real Business DNA analyzer. Without it, generation falls back
# to the deterministic HeuristicGenerator automatically.
OPENAI_API_KEY=""
OPENAI_DNA_MODEL=""

# ------------------------------------------------------------------ Voice (live "Talk to Ava" — ADR-0017)
# Retell is the concrete VoiceProvider. Without RETELL_API_KEY, the call experience
# shows an honest "not connected" state rather than a fake conversation. This is
# the only variable that actually gates a feature.
RETELL_API_KEY=""
RETELL_DEFAULT_VOICE_ID=""
RETELL_LLM_MODEL=""
# Must be a PUBLICLY reachable base URL — Retell calls back to it to execute tools
# mid-call. A bare localhost dev server needs a tunnel (e.g. ngrok) for live tool
# calls (booking, lookup, etc.) to work; without it, session creation still
# succeeds but Ava cannot complete bookings. On Vercel this is auto-derived from
# the request host, so it's only needed for custom-domain edge cases.
PUBLIC_APP_URL=""

# ------------------------------------------------------------------ Booking CTA
# External scheduling link for the closing "Book a demo" CTA. Falls back to a
# mailto: link if unset.
NEXT_PUBLIC_BOOKING_URL=""

# ------------------------------------------------------------------ App
NODE_ENV="development"
